\v 7 Ngalesosikhathi kuzalethwa isipho\x + Hlab. 68.29. 2 Lan. 32.23. Hlab. 68.31. Zef. 3.10.\x* eN\nd kosi\nd*ni yamabandla, isizwe eside lesibutshelezi\x + 18.7.\x*, lesizweni esesabekayo kusukela lapho kusiya phambili\x + 18.7.\x*, isizwe esingumzilamzila esinyathelela phansi\x + 18.7.\x*, esilizwe laso imifula iyalehlukanisa\x + 18.7.\x*, siye endaweni yebizo leN\nd kosi\nd* yamabandla, intaba yeZiyoni.